      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAST COMMAND (1) had been improving with racing this preparation and that culminated with a dominant Eagle Farm victory last time out. Gets 2kg off with the claim and should get the run of the race from gate two. Can go back-to-back. RAMP IT UP (4) has a win and a second from two attempts over this track and trip and will be at peak fitness now fourth-up. Rates highly on best figures. The well-related WILD GYPSY (6) (half to G1 winner Wild Ruler and G3 winner Pavrita) returned to the winners' stall at the latest outing and will have taken some confidence from that victory. Include in calculations. PIREONTI (8) returned in good order with a solid Sunny Coast win and Bayliss sticks in the irons. In the mix. VICTORY COMMAND (3) rounds out the selections in a race with only a handful of chances.",
